          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧进，参。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参过菩萨，徒弟们，撞钟擂鼓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（了然参，坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徒弟们看茶。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（了然上茶。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，师父方才说从东都来的，不知东都至此有多少路程，大唐朝内，可有多少\n文武，在路行程，不知过了多少府县，光景如何？望师父试说一遍，贫僧洗耳\n恭听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老师父听禀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（驻马听） 四海同风，圣主英明敏又聪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黎民鱼变，满朝臣宰，尽都是薆龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文修武备把升平诵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万国来同，万国来同。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝呈玉帛，车书一统，车书一统。"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领教了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问师父，宝刹建造多少年了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这观音院呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（驻马听） 许久颓崩，祸宇荒凉，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣像朦，香残火冷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蜗涎鼠糞，断鼓迷钟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那时老僧呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（驻马听） 敲梆募化十檀经，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "重修殿宇把诸神供。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "雕刻鲜明，雕刻鲜明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说，多有领教了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问师父，从天朝来，可带了什么宝贝？求借一看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝贝虽有，只是贫僧远行，不曾带来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，老师父要看宝贝么，待我取来你看。这件锦襕袈裟，可不是宝贝？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（了然看袈裟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，好宝贝。果然的好宝贝。\n啊师父，老僧痴长一百二十余岁，不曾见此宝贝。欲求借与老僧细观一宵，明\n早奉还，不知师父意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老师父要细看看不妨拿去，明早还我就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请到禅堂用斋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，老师父，我那马呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呕，是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要你好生喂养。"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个自然。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧、孙悟空同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呀，好宝贝。真个人生罕有。怎么设个法儿，谋了他的才好。有了，不免唤\n出徒弟们来，大家想个计策。\n徒弟们哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众僧人同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来咧，来咧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧人",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听师父叫，慌忙就来到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，有何吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，徒弟们，今有大唐来了两个和尚，带来一件锦襕袈裟，真乃人间罕有的宝\n贝！你们大家看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众僧人同看，同夸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，徒弟们，我如今要谋下此宝留在本院，作一个传家之宝，咱们大家想个计\n策。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大家想来。\n有咧，有咧，又碰回去咧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，有了，我把袈裟藏在韦陀龛内，你们到了三更时分，四面上放起火来，将\n他们师徒烧死，得了袈裟重修庙宇，再塑金身。有何不可？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好计策，好计策。"
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "了然",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放下一星火，"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧人",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "能烧万层山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（了然、众僧人同下。孙悟空上，听。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀好贼秃！这等凶狠，你要将俺师徒烧死，怎得能够。俺不免将火神召来。\n呔！火神速降。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（火神上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "火神",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三眼狰狞相轩昂，金鞭举处鬼神寒。火轮展破红莲地，勅命南方火德权。"
        },
        {
          "character": "火神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾乃火德星君是也。今有大圣相召，须速前往。\n呔！火部众神，就此驾云前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众神",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "火神",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忙忙的——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（斗鹌鹑） 驾云乘风，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "须度了云山几重。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫咱去相从。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎肯向污地栽种，污地栽种。"
        },
        {
          "character": "火神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大圣请了。相召吾神，有何见谕？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，无事也不劳动于你，只为那寺的了然秃廝，今夜三更时分，要将我师徒烧\n死咧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "火神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇呀，哇呀呀呀呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（金蕉叶） 听说罢，不由人心中气涌，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "顷刻间，一个个头焦额红。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真个是，杀人可恕，情理难容。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还要借你的火罩，将俺师父的睡处罩住，不要惊动于他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "火神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大圣放心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "火神",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺、俺、俺，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秃廝儿） 俺将这神罩起空，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "稳睡到日东升。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是当耍的呀，你也要小心着。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "火神 （秃廝儿） 大圣你休谆谆嘱重重，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无惊少恐，无惊少恐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他将袈裟藏在韦陀龛内，这殿也不要烧毁了哇！去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "火神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（圣药王） 西天界如来用，如来用，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "腾空烈焰不让些儿缝。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "把残生断送。"
        },
        {
          "character": "火神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "火神",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万事到头总成空，齐付南柯一梦中，一梦中。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人自两边分下。）"
        }
      ],
